'''奧林匹亞體育場'''（Stadium at Olympia）是[[希臘|希臘]][[奧林匹亞|奧林匹亞]]的一座古代體育場遺址，位於[[奧林匹亞宙斯神廟|奧林匹亞宙斯神廟]]東側。這座體育場是[[古代奧林匹克運動會|古代奧林匹克運動會]]眾多體育比賽的舉辦場地。[[2004年奧林匹克運動會|2004年奧林匹克運動會]]期間，這裡是鉛球比賽的舉辦場地。<ref>{{cite news| url=https://www.arabnews.com/sports/news/913701| title=Flame for Rio Olympics is lit at birthplace of ancient Games| agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]| date=21 April 2016| newspaper=[[Arab_News|Arab News]]| location=Riyadh| quote=...the ceremony continued in the ancient stadium — which was used at the 2004 Athens Games as the shot put venue.| accessdate=2020-09-21| archive-date=2016-06-07| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160607113745/http://www.arabnews.com/sports/news/913701| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2004/aug/19/athensolympics2004.athletics2| title=Ancient and modern Shot put revisits Olympia| date=19 August 2004| access-date=12 March 2020| work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]| location=London| archive-date=2019-04-10| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190410214613/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2004/aug/19/athensolympics2004.athletics2| dead-url=no}}</ref>

